Package: athyrta
Type: Package
Title: Data Downloading and Caching
Version: 0.0.0-2
Author: Andrew Marx
Maintainer: Andrew Marx <ajm.rpackages@gmail.com>
Description: Tool for downloading and caching data from web apps or other remote
    sources with a compatible API. Currently a proof-of-concept in the alpha stage
    of development for internal and private use, with the expectation that future
    releases will be suitable for third-party use.
